      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the atmosphere, but it feels a bit generic. I want to get more specific with the actual people in the scene to really ground that tension. Can you add some details about the types of people hanging out on the corners or walking through these streets? I want to see the \"danger\" reflected in the characters—what are they wearing, what are they doing, and what's the vibe they're giving off to someone walking through?",
